ActFishing and Recreational Harbours Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Fishing and Recreational Harbours Regulations (Miscellaneous Program)
PrecisRegulations amending the FISHING AND RECREATIONAL HARBOURS REGULATIONS (MISCELANEOUS PROGRAM) (FRHR) in order to (1) update the list of harbours in Schedule I of the FRHR to a) remove harbours recently divested by Fisheries and Oceans Canada (DFO); b) add harbours recently acquired by (DFO); c) correct the names or locations of currently listed harbours; and (2) update the three references to “Newfoundland” in the FRHR to the official name of the province, which is “Newfoundland and Labrador”.
